Brussels had commissioned the independent scientific committee in view of the widespread use of portable musical instruments among young people.
"Scientists - this concludes the EU communication - confirm that there is a proper concern and that the European Commission, together with the other members of the European Union and those concerned, will now examine the necessary measures to better protect children and young people from the noise, from portable music devices and similar devices."
